00:15:34,228 --> 00:15:36,630
And again, we're gonna bucket it just like before.

308
00:15:36,630 --> 00:15:39,251
We're gonna take all of the players who experienced a

309
00:15:40,072 --> 00:15:44,716
gap of up to 50 throughout all their matches for every single match and see whether or not they

