00:17:23,852 --> 00:17:25,353
that they're just not gonna win this match.

344
00:17:25,353 --> 00:17:26,754
What'll happen, right?

345
00:17:26,754 --> 00:17:29,375
So if the team skill gap is important,

346
00:17:29,375 --> 00:17:32,536
then again, we'd expect something like this.

