00:17:35,397 --> 00:17:37,058
and it turns out that the blue team

350
00:17:37,058 --> 00:17:39,578
is worse than the red team, so much worse,

351
00:17:39,578 --> 00:17:41,319
that they can feel pretty early on

352
00:17:41,319 --> 00:17:43,120
that they're not going to win,

353
00:17:43,120 --> 00:17:45,801
and this causes them to disengage, and they leave.

354
00:17:46,274 --> 00:17:50,778
This is potentially even worse than the single player quitting out because now we can have

