00:17:50,778 --> 00:17:56,182
several players quitting out of a match. And we want to do a similar observational study in our

356
00:17:56,182 --> 00:18:02,067
data to see if this happens as well. To see if players are going to leave early because they

357
00:18:02,067 --> 00:18:07,732
just can't win. They might as well just leave. So again let's get our data together. We want

358
00:18:07,732 --> 00:18:13,256
players and we want to know for this match what was the team skill gap.

359
00:18:14,065 --> 00:18:15,126
and then did they leave?

360
00:18:15,126 --> 00:18:16,867
So it's very similar to our last one,

