00:22:29,727 --> 00:22:34,991
So we have objects, we have events that are in our skill system that are also important to how

444
00:22:34,991 --> 00:22:41,877
players are able to engage within a match. So and again, having this data available also makes the

445
00:22:41,877 --> 00:22:46,621
system much more quickly figure out how good our players are, so that when we're looking at those

