00:23:17,697 --> 00:23:20,282
We've seen that personal skill gap is important in Halo 5.

459
00:23:20,282 --> 00:23:25,231
We found that we were able to get a four times drop in quit rates

460
00:23:25,231 --> 00:23:27,495
by matchmaking carefully on that personal skill gap.

461
00:23:28,543 --> 00:23:30,704
Also, team skill gap is important.

