00:33:49,418 --> 00:33:52,120
as important for matchmaking sort of fell off for us,

681
00:33:52,120 --> 00:33:54,461
which kind of shows us that at least in Halo 5,

682
00:33:54,461 --> 00:33:57,183
we should focus on those team and personal skill gaps.

