00:34:02,543 --> 00:34:05,704
but it means that our current sort of guidelines

686
00:34:05,704 --> 00:34:07,925
on those other objects are pretty on latency

687
00:34:07,925 --> 00:34:09,746
and on wait time are already pretty good.

688
00:34:09,746 --> 00:34:11,627
And you should be able to discover this as well

