00:34:16,329 --> 00:34:17,670
So again, choose a characteristic,

693
00:34:17,670 --> 00:34:19,390
something that you think is important

694
00:34:19,390 --> 00:34:20,531
or may be important to your players

695
00:34:20,531 --> 00:34:21,672
and you wanna find out.

